Installing Guide for Mandarin Learning Tool for exclusive API and packages

$ pip install googletrans

$ pip install Pillow

$ pip install pinyin

$ pip install gTTS

$ pip install playsound

$ pip install PyDictionary

Get Mandarin Keyboard:

System Preferences -> Keyboard -> Input Sources -> +(add) -> Chinese, Simplified -> Pinyin -> add

Access Keyboard:

Next to battery sign at the top right of mac screen -> click the canadian flag -> switch to pinyin

